rlo_Munich_2-512x768.jpg 512w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2012/01/Don-Carlo_Munich_2-270x405.jpg 270w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2012/01/Don-Carlo_Munich_2.jpg 640w" sizes="(max-width: 133px) 100vw, 133px" /></li><li class="gallery-item"><img width="290" height="186" src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2012/01/Don-Carlo_Munich_1-290x186.jpg" class="attachment-medium size-medium" alt="Don Carlo_Munich_1" srcset="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2012/01/Don-Carlo_Munich_1-290x186.jpg 290w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2012/01/Don-Carlo_Munich_1-270x173.jpg 270w, http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2012/01/Don-Carlo_Munich_1.jpg 960w" sizes="(max-width: 290px) 100vw, 290px" /></li></ul></div></div> <br /> </em></p><p>&nbsp;</p> <a class="wpptopdf" target="_blank" rel="noindex,nofollow" href="http://www.gbopera.it/2012/01/monaco-di-baviera-bayerische-staatsoper-don-carlo/?format=pdf" title="Download PDF"><img alt="Download PDF" src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/plugins/wp-post-to-pdf/asset/images/pdf.png"></a></div><div class="clear"></div><div class="entry-extra clearfix"><div class="comments-link " style="color: #363636"> <i class="icon-comment"></i> <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/2012/01/monaco-di-baviera-bayerische-staatsoper-don-carlo/#respond"><span class="leave-reply" style="color:#363636 !important;">Leave a reply</span></a></div><div class="entry-share"> <span style="color: #363636">Share This<i class="icon-plus"></i></span><div class="entry-share-icons"> <span class="ct-pinterest" title="Share on Pinterest"><a href="http://pinterest.com/pin/create/button/?url=http://www.gbopera.it/2012/01/monaco-di-baviera-bayerische-staatsoper-don-carlo/&amp;media=http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2012/01/Don-Carlo-Monaco.jpg&amp;description=Monaco%20di%20Baviera,%20Bayerische%20Staatsoper:%20&#8220;Don%20Carlo&#8221;" target="_blank"><i class="icon-pinterest"></i></a></span> <span class="ct-fb" title=