Eric Halfvarson</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/giuseppe-verdi/" rel="tag">Giuseppe Verdi</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/jonas-kaufmann/" rel="tag">jonas kaufmann</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/jurgen-rose/" rel="tag">Jurgen Rose</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/michael-bauer/" rel="tag">Michael Bauer</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/monaco-di-baviera/" rel="tag">Monaco di Baviera</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/opera-lirica/" rel="tag">Opera lirica</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/rene-pape/" rel="tag">René Pape</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/soren-eckhoff/" rel="tag">Soren Eckhoff</a>, <a href="http://www.gbopera.it/tag/steven-humes/" rel="tag">Steven Humes</a><meta itemprop="keywords" content="Anja Harteros, Anna Smirnova, Asher Fisch, Bayerische Staatsoper, Boaz Daniel, Don Carlo, Eric Halfvarson, Giuseppe Verdi, jonas kaufmann, Jurgen Rose, Michael Bauer, Monaco di Baviera, Opera lirica, René Pape, Soren Eckhoff, Steven Humes"> </span> </footer></div> </article><div id="author-block" class="box-shadow-2px clearfix" itemscope="" itemtype="http://schema.org/Person"><h2 class="author-title">About the author</h2><div id="author-avatar"> <img itemprop="image" style="display:none;" src="http://gravatar.com/avatar/a7f83b34427edaaa3e1315bc20e423f4" alt="" /> <img src="http://www.gbopera.it/wp-content/uploads/2013/12/Alice-Zhang-103x150.jpg" width="69" height="100" alt="Alice Zhang" class="avatar avatar-100 wp-user-avatar wp-user-avatar-100 alignnone photo" /></div><div id="author-description" class="padding-20"><meta itemprop="name" content="Alice Zhang"><meta itemprop="url" content=""><p></p><p class="add-author-info"> <a href="#"><i class="icon-facebook-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-twitter-sign"></i></a><a href="#"><i class="icon-google-plus-sign"></i></a></p> <a style="font-size: 11px;" href="http://www.gbopera.it/author/alice-zhang/">View all articles by Alice Zhang</a></div></div><div clas